additional_house_rules:
***Adhere to the Golden Rule: One should treat others as one would like others to treat oneself. In other words, one should not treat others in ways that one would not like to be treated.

This is a smoke-free apartment. Anyone who smokes in the apt will be assessed a $250 Apartment Recovery Fee.

There is a $250 replacement key charge for lost keys and a extra day charge if your bags are not packed and set to the side by noon. 

Additional Guests: Please follow the guidelines for the maximum number of guests allowed at the property. If it's discovered that the number of guests in your party exceeded the maximum allowed, a penalty of $25 per additional guest/per night will be deducted from the security deposit.  You are welcome to check beforehand to see if an additional guest can be accommodated.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

***Adhérer à la règle d'or: Nous devrions traiter les autres comme on aimerait que les autres de s'offrir. En d'autres termes, il ne faut pas traiter les autres de manière que l'on ne voudrait pas être traitée.

Les clients: S'il vous plaît suivre les directives pour le nombre maximum de personnes autorisées à la propriété. Si elle a découvert que le nombre de personnes dans votre parti a dépassé le maximum autorisé, une pénalité de 25 $ par personne supplémentaire / par nuit sera déduit de la caution. Vous êtes invités à vérifier à l'avance pour voir si une personne supplémentaire peut être logée.

Cumplir con la Regla de Oro: Se debe tratar a otros como a uno le gustaría que otros a sí mismo el tratamiento. En otras palabras, uno no debe tratar a los demás de manera que uno no le gustaría ser tratado.

Invitados Adicionales: Por favor, siga las directrices para el número máximo de personas permitidas en la propiedad. Si se descubre que el número de personas en su grupo excede el máximo permitido, una multa de $ 25 por persona adicional / por noche se deducirá de la fianza. Le invitamos a comprobar de antemano para ver si una persona adicional se puede acomodar.

Aderite alla regola d'oro: Una persona dovrebbe trattare gli altri come vorrebbe che gli altri lo trattassero. In altre parole una persona non dovrebbe fare agli altri ciò che non vorrebbe fosse fatto a lui.

Gli ospiti aggiuntivi: Si prega di seguire le linee guida per il numero massimo di ospiti ammessi presso la struttura. Se è scoperto che il numero di ospiti nel suo partito ha superato il massimo consentito, una penale di $ 25 per ogni ospite aggiuntivo / notte verrà detratto dal deposito cauzionale. Siete invitati a verificare in anticipo per vedere se un ospite supplementare può essere accettata.
description:
You'll love staying at my fantastic apt in an elevator building (a rarity for the East Village)! Perfect for groups, or a couple that wants to spread out! This is a hip, vibrant area with European Flare, and more shopping/bars/restaurants than you an imagine! Walk a few blocks and find yourself in the heart of Greenwich Village; a short ride on the subway will put you in Times Square/Rockefeller Center. I love my neighborhood for it's artsy vibe, but it's also super convenient for tourists:)

I love helping people discover NYC, so please do not hesitate to ask for tips and advice, etc! I keep the apt. very clean and ask you do so as well. 

BEDROOM #1:

- Olympic queen-size bed (1) 
- Full-sized bed
- Nice Closet and chest of drawers
- Multiple full-body mirrors 

SECOND BEDROOM:
- Full Size Bed
- Chest of Drawers
- comfy lounging sofa

LIVING ROOM:
- Office Desk for writing / work, electrical outlet
- Large pullout sofabed
- Flatscreen TV
- Breakfast Bar with seating for 6.

MORE ABOUT THE APARTMENT:
- Central Air conditioning & Heating 
- All bed sheets, pillows, blankets, towels included 
- Fully equipped, clean kitchen 
- Light breakfast (cereal). 
- Free High-speed WIFI 
- Complimentary tea and coffee 
- 1 bathroom with a bathtub (that is listed as hot tub in the amenities section).

Guests have access to the entire private apartment.

I am available to answer my guest's questions throughout their stay.

Live like a New Yorker in a private East Village apartment. As soon as you step out of the front door, you are immediately immersed in the lively energy of the City. Perfect for pub/bar/clubs lovers! Walk few blocks and you find yourself in the hustle and bustle of Union Square, Stuyvesant town, Gramercy Park, Tompkins park, Lower East Side, NoHo. Little Italy, SoHo, Chinatown, the West Village, NYU, Union Square and even the famous Chinatown market! I have called this area home for many years, and it truly is a fantastic launching pad to exploring the City!

We are a 5 minute walk to the subway on 14th Street. Easy to hail a cab in my area since it's very popular, night or day:)

An electronic keypad entry allows for easier access to my apartment.

hosts.about: Hello Airbnb community! I am an actress who lives between New York and LA. I love travel, cooking, and staying active. New York is a wonderful city with so much to explore and learn, and I like helping my guests have the best experience possible:) When you stay with me, you'll always get a clean and well-prepared home, thanks to my wonderful cleaner who is super thorough. I take great pride in being a fantastic host.
